                      </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="subtitle">
                      When you choose Care and Relief Foundation, you are
                      assured that your payments are handled with care,
                      integrity, and adherence to Islamic principles.
                    </p>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
